snippet.title: Lady Gaga is Failure at Face Paint -- Fashion Offenders for Aug. 16, 2013
snippet.description:
Lady Gaga, Amber Heard, and Katy Perry all get an F on Fashion Offenders hosted by Wonderwall's Kirby Kristen. 
SUBSCRIBE: http://goo.gl/usQSdP

Lady Gaga was attacked by a paintball gun. Amber Heard's outfit is unflattering. Katy Perry is stuck in the 90s.

About the series: Despite their entourages of specialists, celebs make fashion blunders just like the rest of us. Take a look as Wonderwall showcases the worst fashion fails of the week in just 60 seconds! Don't forget to tune in each week to find out if your favorite celebrity will score an F on "Fashion Offenders," hosted by Kirby Kristen.
